==English==

===Etymology===
From an alteration of [[I'd]] [[rather]] or [['d]] rather.

===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-druthers.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Noun===
'''druthers''' (nearly always plural)
#[[wish|Wishes]], [[preference]]s, or [[way]]s.
#:''If I had my '''druthers''' I’d eat in a restaurant every night of the week.''

